Company Overview of Alma Hospitality Group LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Alma Hospitality Group LLC owns and operates a café and restaurant in Minneapolis, Minnesota. The company offers dining services with a pre-fix three-course menu alongside a wine list, as well as private dining spaces through its restaurant. It also provides drink, snack, or meal options; and rooms for neighborhood gatherings through its café. In addition, the company operates a hotel that provides accommodation services for guests. The company was incorporated in 1999 and is headquartered in Minneapolis, Minnesota.


