Welcome to Palma Hospitality Group.

                                    Established in 2012, Palma Hospitality Group has quickly
                                    established itself as a formidable player within the hospitality
                                    industry in Doha. Our aim is visionary – to be a leading Qatari
                                    company within our areas of operation which include fine
                                    dining, franchising, kids care and education, food and beverage
                                    solutions, consultancy and healthcare. We will achieve this
                                    goal through our commitment to excellence, our passion for
                                    management, and the professionalism of our team.
                                














































































Our Restaurants


                                        At Palma Group we understand that good food and a memorable experience are
                                        what makes our outlets a success. From our established brands, latest openings at
                                        Medina Centrale – The Pearl Qatar to our new Healthy Eating concepts, we make
                                        every meal, treat or coffee an experience to enjoy.
                                    





Franchises


                                        provides the cornerstone of excellent management and prestige brands and
                                        sub-brands. Our partners are wholly supported in their ventures through our consultancy advice, high
